{"analytics_identifier":"IM333","base_path":"/government/organisations/judicial-appointments-and-conduct-ombudsman","content_id":"26e55584-4db9-4476-a527-a3c5cb1eb6d2","description":"We can look at complaints about how investigating bodies have handled complaints alleging misconduct by judicial office holders. We also look at the handling of complaints about the judicial appointments process. JACO works with the Ministry of Justice .","details":{"acronym":"JACO","alternative_format_contact_email":"","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>We can look at complaints about how investigating bodies have handled complaints alleging misconduct by judicial office holders. We also look at the handling of complaints about the judicial appointments process.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Judicial Appointments and Conduct Ombudsman\">JACO</abbr> works with the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/ministry-of-justice\">Ministry of Justice</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"ministry-of-justice","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"custom","formatted_title":"Judicial Appointments and <br/>Conduct Ombudsman","image":{"alt_text":"Judicial Appointments and Conduct Ombudsman","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/59fa00eaed915d7bfdf0a2a8/Judicial_Appointments_and_Conduct_Ombudsman_logo_2.jpg"}},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/judicial-appointments-and-conduct-ombudsman/about/complaints-procedure","title":"Complaints procedure"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"News story","href":"https://www.gov.uk/government/news/appointment-of-the-judicial-appointments-and-conduct-ombudsman","image":{"alt_text":"Douglas Marshall","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/604b67e7e90e071536434f05/s712_Doug_Marshall_Picture.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/604b67e78fa8f505da05af13/s465_Doug_Marshall_Picture.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/604b67e78fa8f505d99b4717/Doug_Marshall_Picture.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2021-03-04T00:00:00.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Lord Chancellor has announced the appointment of the Judicial Appointments and Conduct Ombudsman.</p>\n</div>","title":"Appointment of the Judicial Appointments and Conduct Ombudsman "}],"ordered_featured_links":[{"href":"https://jaco.form.service.justice.gov.uk/","title":"Judicial conduct investigations complaints"},{"href":"https://judicial-appointments-commission-complaint.form.service.justice.gov.uk/","title":"Judicial appointment complaints"},{"href":"https://judicial-conduct-investigations-complaint-joh.form.service.justice.gov.uk/","title":"Judicial conduct investigations complaint - Judicial Office Holders Only"},{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/reasonable-adjustment-policy","title":"Reasonable Adjustments Policy"}],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organisation_featuring_priority":"news","organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null},"organisation_political":false,"organisation_type":"other","secondary_corporate_information_pages":"","social_media_links":[]},"document_type":"organisation","first_published_at":"2012-02-29T11:17:20+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"analytics_identifier":"IM333","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/judicial-appointments-and-conduct-ombudsman","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/judicial-appointments-and-conduct-ombudsman","base_path":"/government/organisations/judicial-appointments-and-conduct-ombudsman","content_id":"26e55584-4db9-4476-a527-a3c5cb1eb6d2","document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-02-16T10:47:15Z","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Judicial Appointments and Conduct Ombudsman","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/judicial-appointments-and-conduct-ombudsman","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_board_members":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/douglas-marshall","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/douglas-marshall","base_path":"/government/people/douglas-marshall","content_id":"bda591d4-d8e8-4c22-a9df-ba1b8377ac05","details":{"image":{"alt_text":"Douglas Marshall","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6049e9778fa8f54016d724d7/s465_Doug_Marshall_Picture.jpg"},"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","links":{"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"fc92f85e-cef8-4dbd-b476-e7f22e4ab70a","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":6691,"started_on":"2021-03-01T00:00:00+00:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"8472e69b-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The ombudsman investigates complaints about the judicial appointments process and the way in which judicial discipline or conduct has been handled.</p>\n\n<p>There are 2 unique responsibilities that form part of the role and the investigative process.</p>\n\n<p>These are to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>seek an appropriate solution in the event of maladministration (ie mismanagement), which includes, among other things: delay, rudeness, bias, incorrect procedures, misleading advice and unfair treatment</li>\n  <li>help organisations develop better ways of dealing with complaints about judicial appointments or judicial misconduct</li>\n</ul>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2014-06-23T10:07:20Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Judicial Appointments and Conduct Ombudsman","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2021-03-11T09:59:56Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Douglas Marshall - Judicial Appointments and Conduct Ombudsman","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2021-03-11T09:58:33Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Douglas Marshall","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/douglas-marshall","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_contacts":[{"content_id":"96d265b2-a0ad-4897-b1de-f778f45e7e9b","details":{"contact_form_links":null,"description":"The Judicial Appointments and Conduct Ombudsman’s office is not fully staffed and mostly working remotely. The impact of this is that we may take longer to consider complaints and deal with correspondence. The best way to contact the office during this period is by email at headofoffice@judicialombudsman.gov.uk.\r\n\r\nIf you need to speak to a member of the team urgently, please send us an email requesting a call back – please include your contact number and a brief explanation of your query. A member of the team will contact you as soon as possible. Please note we cannot help you with a Court or Tribunal case, investigate a judicial office holder or say whether their actions amount to misconduct.\r\n\r\nWe will process personal data in accordance with our Privacy Notice.","email_addresses":[{"email":"Headofoffice@judicialombudsman.gov.uk"}],"phone_numbers":null,"post_addresses":[{"iso2_country_code":"gb","locality":"London","postal_code":"SW1H 9AJ","street_address":"Office of the Judicial Appointments and Conduct Ombudsman\r\nPostal Point 1.55\r\n1st Floor, the Tower\r\n102 petty France\r\n","world_location":"United Kingdom"}],"title":"General Enquiries"},"document_type":"contact","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2021-09-03T07:43:46Z","schema_name":"contact","title":"General Enquiries","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_parent_organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"D18","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/ministry-of-justice","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/ministry-of-justice","base_path":"/government/organisations/ministry-of-justice","content_id":"dcc907d6-433c-42df-9ffb-d9c68be5dc4d","details":{"acronym":"MOJ","brand":"ministry-of-justice","default_news_image":{"high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5a37db21ed915d5a62fdc762/s960_ministry-of-justice.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5a37db21e5274a7908e352d9/s300_ministry-of-justice.jpg"},"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Ministry<br/>of Justice"},"organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null}},"document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Ministry of Justice","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/ministry-of-justice","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_roles":[{"content_id":"8472e69b-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The ombudsman investigates complaints about the judicial appointments process and the way in which judicial discipline or conduct has been handled.</p>\n\n<p>There are 2 unique responsibilities that form part of the role and the investigative process.</p>\n\n<p>These are to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>seek an appropriate solution in the event of maladministration (ie mismanagement), which includes, among other things: delay, rudeness, bias, incorrect procedures, misleading advice and unfair treatment</li>\n  <li>help organisations develop better ways of dealing with complaints about judicial appointments or judicial misconduct</li>\n</ul>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2014-06-23T10:07:20Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Judicial Appointments and Conduct Ombudsman","withdrawn":false}],"organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"IM333","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/judicial-appointments-and-conduct-ombudsman","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/judicial-appointments-and-conduct-ombudsman","base_path":"/government/organisations/judicial-appointments-and-conduct-ombudsman","content_id":"26e55584-4db9-4476-a527-a3c5cb1eb6d2","details":{"acronym":"JACO","brand":"ministry-of-justice","default_news_image":null,"logo":{"crest":"custom","formatted_title":"Judicial Ap